text: Hansueli Schmutz (born 26 July 1950) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Basel-Landschaft
